{"id":28149,"date":[{"year":1938,"month":8,"day":23}],"page":"11","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"灯塔","column":"问答栏:,大众信箱","genre":"","count":"74","ytitle":"","mtitle":"遇水而化","ftitle":"","authors":["寒梅"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲:这一双泥腿倒底会陷吗?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙:不会陷的。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲:何以?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙:因为泥是遇水而化，黄河水化一半，长江水化它一半，已是无腿可陷了。"}]}